NOTICE — Third-party content

This repository's `skills/workflow/references/` directory contains 14 language and
framework style guides (alibaba-java, bulletproof-react, airbnb-javascript-style,
google-typescript-style, etc.) which are copyrighted by their respective authors.
They are included for personal reference and learning purposes only and are NOT
covered by the MIT License above.

`skills/workflow/references/agent-principles.md` and `skills/workflow/references/frontend-aesthetics.md`
contain prompts from Anthropic's official Claude Code documentation
(https://code.claude.com/docs/). These are copyrighted by Anthropic and included
for personal study only.

If this repository is ever published to a public marketplace or open-source
community, the maintainer must:

1. Clean up or replace the `references/` directory with original content
2. Remove or significantly rewrite the Anthropic prompt references
3. Update this NOTICE and the License section in README.md accordingly
